<FONT color=#33cc00>hey everyone, i'm doing my spainish homework. finals are next week, paul is having a baby girl and he's naming her torance/tori. whatever, so um, life has been a lil bumpy but i hope it flatens out soon. i wanna eat something, hmm... but i'm too lazy to get of my seat. so um, yeah, i get my yearbooks tomorrow. i'm exceted, monday will be a sad day cuz we r cleaning out our lockers. i love my locker. i's so great. this year has gone by pretty fast. 1/4th of my high school career is done! i'm pretty exceted for next year cuz i wont get all that shit for being a freshman. but my schedual is packed! i have chemistry, honors english, algebra 2 honors, world history and spanish 2. i have my work cut out for me. sheesh. i'm so fucking sad cuz Mia is moving away. i can't even think about that. wow, now that i look back at this year i realize how many great things have happened. this was really a great first year of high school, but i would never what to relive it. EVER. lol. i learned so much. hahah at this point i would have clicked out of this, i just keep babbling on and on. i'm really nervous about finals. it should be interesting. sigghh. i won by debate today in biology! JOY. it was so great, we won by one point. lol. close ehh? it was on whether or not genetic research will improve health care. it was just trilling. even though i had to go against brittany, one of my best friends. she got back stage passes to warped tour and is taking erin, daytona, and sari. she is tring to get another one for me cuz her dad is a sound guy who will be working there. i feel kinda left out but it's all good i guess cuz i have tickest already and it's more fun in the mosh. lol. they will be up on the side of the stage w/ the band(s) thats pretty fucking cool too though. oh well. they can watch me in my true colors. lol. wow i have wrote a lot. i best be getting to my homeowrk . good bye my furry friends! </FONT>
